      "widgets_values": [
        "rdhlk, the colossal red gamma-powered super soldier, is captured mid-air during a dynamic, wide-angle cinematic shot. In a futuristic, war-torn city under a cloudy, smoky sky, rdhlk, with his massive organic crimson right arm and his complex, intricate silver cybernetic left arm, is locked in intense combat. He is smashing his powerful bionic fist into the central processor of a large, bulky, bipedal military robot with glowing red optical sensors. His facial expression is fierce and determined, eyes glowing, short black hair wild. He wears his navy blue tactical suit with the white star emblem and leather harnesses. Around him, smaller spider-like robots are being knocked aside, sparks, fire, and oil erupting from the mechanical wreckage. Damaged, futuristic skyscrapers fill the background. The scene is illuminated by dramatic low light and electrical flashes, with debris suspended in the air. Highly detailed textures, Unreal Engine 5 style, photorealistic action, dynamic composition, cinematic masterpiece, hyper detailed anatomy, blockbuster movie aesthetic."
      ]
    },
