      "widgets_values": [
        "# 🖼️ Krea 2 Quantized — ComfyUI Quick Setup\n\nAll quantized models (FP8 / MXFP8 / NVFP4 / INT8 / ConvRot INT8) for both Base and Turbo:\n\n👉 **[Winnougan/Krea-2-Base-Turbo-NVFP4-FP8-INT8](https://huggingface.co/Winnougan/Krea-2-Base-Turbo-NVFP4-FP8-INT8)**\n\n---\n\n## Required Downloads\n\n**Text Encoder** — Comfy now supports INT8 text encoders! Load with CLIPLoader, type `krea2`:  \n👉 [qwen3vl_4b_INT8.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Winnougan/Krea-2-Base-Turbo-NVFP4-FP8-INT8/resolve/main/Text%20Encoder/qwen3vl_4b_int8.safetensors)\n\n**VAE** — Same as Anima:  \n👉 [qwen_image_vae.safetensors](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Qwen-Image_ComfyUI/blob/main/split_files/vae/qwen_image_vae.safetensors)\n\n---\n\n## Recommended Settings\n\n| Model | Steps | CFG | Resolution |\n|-------|-------|-----|------------|\n| Turbo | 8 | 0.0 | 1024–2048px |\n| Raw | 52 | 3.5 | up to 1024px |"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
